official_title: To award a Congressional Gold Medal to 60 diplomats, in recognition of their bravery and heroism during the Holocaust.
short_title: Forgotten Heroes of the Holocaust Congressional Gold Medal Act
subjects: War crimes, genocide, crimes against humanity

summary.text:
Forgotten Heroes of the Holocaust Congressional Gold Medal Act

This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to 60 diplomats posthumously in recognition of their brave and vital service of saving Jews during World War II.
